content.rendered: And when I looked to the moon it had turned to gold,. Blue moon, now I’m no longer alone, Without a dream in my heart, Without a love of my own. And then there suddenly appeared before me. The only one my arms will ever hold heard somebody whisper please adore me. And when I looked the Moonhad turned to gold.
